#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In cases were utilities or automatic instrumentation is not available, manual instrumentation can be used to generate spans, propagate the OpenTelemetry context and the Baggage."
msgstr "在无法使用公用工具或自动配置工具的情况下，可以使用手动配置工具来生成跨度，并传播 OpenTelemetry 上下文和 Baggage。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use Manual instrumentation if there are no other alternatives because it will require more maintenance work."
msgstr "如果没有其他选择，请使用手动配置，因为这将需要更多的维护工作。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Manual Span"
msgstr "手动跨度"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "On the following example we have a class with a method implementing a manual span with a custom attribute. The only business logic we are measuring there is the `return \"Hello from Quarkus REST\";` statement."
msgstr "在下面的示例中，我们有一个类，其中包含一个方法，该方法实现了一个带有自定义属性的手动跨度。我们在此处衡量的唯一业务逻辑就是 `返回` 语句 `“Hello from Quarkus REST”。`"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is essential that all the logic the span is measuring be well delimited by a scope. The scope is Autocloseable."
msgstr "span 所测量的所有逻辑必须由一个作用域明确界定。该作用域支持自动关闭。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Manual Context Propagation"
msgstr "手动上下文传播"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When you send messages or requests with clients that don't propagate the OpenTelemetry context you will have incomplete traces or broken traces, when the destination creates spans but because no context was propagated, the parent span is non-existent. This will cause more than one trace per request, which will cause problems."
msgstr "当您使用无法传播 OpenTelemetry 上下文的客户端发送消息或请求时，将会出现不完整的追踪或断裂的追踪。这是因为目标端虽然创建了跨度，但由于未传播上下文，导致父跨度不存在。这将导致每个请求产生多个追踪，从而引发问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Manual propagation can be implemented for those clients if there is a way to ship metadata containing the OpenTelemetry context with the message or request."
msgstr "如果能够将包含 OpenTelemetry 上下文的元数据随消息或请求一并发送，则可以针对这些客户端实现手动传播。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*This is an advanced subject*. For more details on context propagation please check the above section about <<propagators-reference>>."
msgstr "*这是一个高级主题* 。有关上下文传播的更多详细信息，请参阅上文关于 <<propagators-reference>> 的部分。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Next, we have an implementation example. The class contains a `MAP_SETTER`, a `MAP_GETTER` and 2 methods."
msgstr "接下来，我们来看一个实现示例。该类包含一个 `MAP_SETTER` 、一个 `MAP_GETTER` 以及 2 个方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `MAP_SETTER` handles how to store data in the carrier map that will transport the context."
msgstr "`MAP_SETTER` 负责处理如何将数据存储在用于传输上下文的载体映射中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`MAP_GETTER` handles how to retrieve data from the carrier map transporting the context."
msgstr "`MAP_GETTER` 负责处理如何从承载上下文的载体地图中检索数据。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `createParentContext()` method explains how to create an OpenTelemetry context. In this case we generate the default https://www.w3.org/TR/trace-context/[W3C Trace Context] header: `traceparent`."
msgstr "`createParentContext()` 方法介绍了如何创建一个 OpenTelemetry 上下文。在此情况下，我们会生成默认的 link:https://www.w3.org/TR/trace-context/[W3C 跟踪上下文] 标头： `traceparent` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "the `receiveAndUseContext()` method receives the contents of the `traceparent` header used to bootstrap a new OpenTelemetry context in the destination."
msgstr "`receiveAndUseContext()` 方法接收 `traceparent` 标头的内容，该内容用于在目标端初始化一个新的 OpenTelemetry 上下文。"

#. type: Title ==
