#, fuzzy
msgid "Manual Baggage propagation"
msgstr "手提行李的传播"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/api/#baggage[Baggage] can be used to send application specific data using the OpenTelemetry's propagation mechanism."
msgstr "link:https://opentelemetry.io/docs/languages/java/api/#baggage[Baggage] 可用于通过 OpenTelemetry 的传播机制发送应用程序特定数据。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/opentelemetry-tracing.adoc
