msgid "In Quarkus, as documented in the <<cdi-injections-reference>>, Baggage can be injected to unwrap data coming with inbound requests but in more complex scenarios were data needs to be sent away in the Baggage manual instrumentation is required."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 中，正如《 <<cdi-injections-reference>> 》中所述，可以通过注入 Baggage 来解析传入请求中的数据；但在更复杂的情景下，如果需要将数据通过 Baggage 发送出去，则需要手动进行配置。"

